title: IvraQuell
---
Ivra: Keep the ship flying, keep the crew breathing, and don't waste a clean launch window.
-> Repair Ship
    Ivra: I can clear the hull wear if the station ledger agrees with your scrap pile.
-> Refit Ship
    Ivra: Yard is open. Make the changes count before the next launch.
===

title: SableRen
---
Sable: Take the jobs that keep us useful. Leave the heroic nonsense to dead captains.
-> Open Contracts
    Sable: The board is current. If a route looks quiet, that means someone forgot to report back.
===

title: PeregrineCho
---
Cho: History here survives in fragments. Bring anything that still speaks.
-> Open Archives
    Cho: The station remembers what crews recover and what they leave behind.
===
